Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.78,0:14:12.88,IN-CH,,0,0,20,,{\an8\fad(300,300)\bord1\blur3}我们仍在逐梦 不论多远也不止步
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.88,0:14:22.78,IN-CH,,0,0,20,,{\an8\fad(300,300)\bord1\blur3}最重要的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.59,0:14:32.15,IN-CH,,0,0,20,,{\an8\fad(300,300)\bord1\blur3}从最初开始 就不曾改变
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.26,0:14:40.22,IN-CH,,0,0,20,,{\an8\fad(300,300)\bord1\blur3}让这歌声 径直向前
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.32,0:14:47.19,IN-CH,,0,0,20,,{\an8\fad(300,300)\bord1\blur3}只愿让你 立刻听到
Comment: 1,0:14:47.31,0:14:49.09,IN-CH,,0,0,20,,{\an8\fad(300,300)\bord1\blur3}song for you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.71,0:14:57.58,IN-CH,,0,0,20,,{\an8\fad(300,300)\bord1\blur3}是你的 你无瑕的目光
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.58,0:15:05.76,IN-CH,,0,0,20,,{\an8\fad(300,300)\bord1\blur3}为我照亮了 这冰冷的世界
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.76,0:15:14.35,IN-CH,,0,0,20,,{\an8\fad(300,300)\bord1\blur3}将这无法抑制的所有心愿
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.35,0:15:23.13,IN-CH,,0,0,20,,{\an8\fad(300,300)\bord1\blur3}化作荣耀 随歌唱响
